text: Browne Lake may refer to: * Browne Lake, a reservoir in Chambers County, Alabama, United States * Browne Lake, a reservoir in Gwinnett County, Georgia, United States * Browne Lake (Utah), a reservoir in Daggett County, Utah, United States * Browne Lake Provincial Park, a park in British Columbia, Canada * Brownes Lake, a reservoir in Beaverhead County, Montana, United States ==See also== * Brown Lake * Browns Lake ==References==
